section.section:
As to these personnel, the county superintendent shall:
Assign them to their positions in the schools;
Transfer them as the needs of the schools require;
Recommend them for promotion; and
Suspend them for cause and recommend them for dismissal in accordance with § 6-202 of this subtitle.

These personnel shall include:
Supervising or helping teachers;
Supervisors of pupil personnel I;
Supervisors of pupil personnel II; and
Visiting teachers.
